"{\"uid\": \"thedailybeast.com-now-paris-olympic-saboteurs-are-targeting-the-phone-lines\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Saboteurs who brought France's high-speed train linesto a standstillbefore theOlympicopening ceremony inParisare being blamed for a series of similar attacks on targets including telecommunications networks.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999746787583, \"rank\": 1.2815808186858364e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities reported damage to fiber-optic networks in six regions of the country, although no major disruption to phone or internet services was reported.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Friday's attacks on the TGV network, there was speculation that Russian security services could be behind the coordinated action as payback for PresidentEmmanuel Macron's military support forUkraine.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TGV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\"}, {\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9998305716038094, \"rank\": 0.00014326651602761037, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.168908165266088e-18, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the arrest on Sunday of what police called an \\\"ultra-left activist\\\" apparently trying to gain access to a network control room belonging to the SNCF train company adds to growing evidence that it is homegrown anti-capitalist protesters who are doing their best to undermine the $9 billion Olympic project.\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A police source toldAFPthat the man detained at Oissel in the northern province of Normandy had keys to SNCF technical premises and a set of universal passkeys.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"score\": 0.9960567020682025, \"rank\": 0.0038713012010406027, \"text\": \"Normandy\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also carrying tools and a copy of an anti-capitalist resistance handbook.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Interior Minister G\\u00e9rald Darmanin said Monday that more than 50 people had been arrested for planning to disrupt the Olympics and said far-left groups were behind the attacks.\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"score\": 0.9999968416907302, \"rank\": 2.8479632538813247e-06, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\", \"score\": 0.9999999823287454, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"G\\u00e9rald Darmanin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forty-five of those are thought to be the environmental group Extinction Rebellion who had been planning to disrupt early Olympic events-and are not necessarily being blamed for the rail and telecoms sabotage.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extinction_Rebellion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Extinction Rebellion\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extinction_Rebellion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extinction_Rebellion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Referring to the sabotage attacks, Darmanin told the France 2 TV channel that it was to early to say who was responsible.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France 2\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the traditional mode of action of the far left,\\\" he said, but added: \\\"We must be careful.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The question is whether they were manipulated or is it for their own benefit.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are people who can approach this movement.\\\"\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the targets was a telecoms relay tower near the southwestern city of Toulouse that was set on fire in the first wave of attacks early on Friday.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearby was found a spray-painted tag \\\"No: J.O.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"-apparently referring to a a hard-left anarchist group that is opposed to theJeux Olympiques, or Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday's attacks disrupted high-speed TGV services from Paris to the rest of the country, as well as Eurostar services to London through the Channel Tunnel.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TGV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\"}, {\"begin\": 2232, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2667812399371682e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999998026358038, \"rank\": 1.9736412320846335e-07, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 2298, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998772847622753, \"rank\": 6.924091231695395e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_Tunnel\", \"score\": 0.9999619605894304, \"rank\": 3.8040857566083854e-05, \"text\": \"Channel Tunnel\", \"types\": [\"Q1311958\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_Tunnel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_Tunnel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But all services were back to normal by Monday after emergency engineering repairs.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"philippe.naughton@thedailybeast.com  Got a tip?\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send it to The Daily Beasthere.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  ADVERTISEMENT\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": []}]}"